Mu kwezi kwa cumi na kabiri 2019, Coronavirus nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV) yatangiye kwandura, ubu ikaba yitwa COVID-2019 (Coronavirus Disease 2019), naho virusi yo muri iki gihe yitwa SARS-CoV-2.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku Buzima wahamije ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo ku isi hose.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryatanze inama ku bijyanye n'ubuvuzi bw'ihindagurika ryashyizwe ahagaragara kuri internet mu kinyamakuru cya Military Medical Research ku wa 6 Gashyantare 2020.
