Urugero, amabwiriza yo gupima no kuvura COVID-19 yasohotse n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu gishinzwe Ubuzima cya Repubulika y'Igihugu y'u Bushinwa (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), kuva ku itariki ya 16 Mutarama 2020 kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, yasohoye ingingo zirindwi, harimo n'izindi zimwe na zimwe z'ibanze zavuguruwe.
