Bangladesh yatangaje abantu batanu bishwe na COVID-19, umubare munini w'abapfuye ku munsi
Mu mujyi wa Dune, Bangladesh hemejwe ko hari abantu batanu baguye muri COVID-19 kuri uwo munsi.
Ni umubare munini w'abapfa ku munsi umwe bahitanywe na virusi.
Ku munsi w'ejo, Ikigo cya Bangladesh cyo kugenzura no gukora ubushakashatsi ku ndwara n'indwara (IEDCR) cyatangaje umubare w'abanduye, harimo 114 banduye n'abakize 33 bari mu rugo.
Hamaze kuboneka abantu 17 bapfuye.
Mu bisobanuro byatanzwe ku rubuga rwa interineti, umuyobozi wa IEDCR, Mirza Saverina Flora yavuze ko abantu bapfuye ari abagabo bane n'umugore umwe.
Dr Mirjard yavuze ko babiri bari hejuru y'imyaka 60, babiri bari hagati y'imyaka 51 na 60, n'undi umwe wari hagati y'imyaka 41 na 50.
Nanone yavuze ko abahitanywe n'ibyo byago bari abantu bo mu mugi wa Daka.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryemeje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo ku isi ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe.
Umukozi w'ubuzima yabwiye ikinyamakuru Anadolu, ikigo cy'amakuru cyo mu gihugu, ko umwe mu bapfuye ari Jalal Sayfur Rahman, umuyobozi wa Komite ya Bangladesh yo kurwanya ruswa, yari ihagarariye ibitaro bya Kuwait City.
Ku wa gatandatu, mu itangazo ry'amashusho kuri interineti, Minisitiri w'Ubucuruzi n'Ubwogero, Abdullahi Qadir yavuze ko imodoka rusange zizagurwa mu gihe kirekire kurusha uko byari biteganyijwe, kugeza ku wa gatandatu utaha.
Imodoka zitwara abantu zitangiye guhagarara ku wa 26 Werurwe, kandi zateganyijwe kurangira ku wa Gatandatu tariki ya 4 Mata.
Ibikoresho bikenewe - imiti, peteroli n'ibiribwa - biracyari mu nzira.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cya mbere cyanditswe muri Bangladesh cyabaye ku wa 8 Werurwe, mu bantu babiri bagarutse mu Butaliyani bari kumwe n'umugore w'umwe muri bo.
Ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe, abo bantu batatu bari bakira.
