Ku wa Gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryemeje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 - icyorezo cyatewe na coronavirus ya SARS-CoV-2 - cyabaye icyorezo ku isi hose.
Nubwo ijambo "icyorezo" ryerekeza gusa ku kuntu indwara yandukira, aho kwerekeza ku kuntu ibintu byihariye bishobora guteza akaga, OMS ivuga ko leta zigomba kugira icyo zikora:
Tedros Adhanom Gabryus, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima (OMS), yavuze ko ibihugu byose bishobora guhindura icyorezo.
Iyo ibihugu byashyizeho abaturage babyo, bibakingira, bibakira, bibarobanura kandi bakabakurikirana.
Dufite impungenge z'uko ibi bikoresho by'ubushakashatsi byashoboraga gukoreshwa mu guhumeka.
Dr Tom Friedin, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika Gishinzwe Kugenzura no Kurinda Indwara, yavuze ko icyorezo "kitari cyitezwe".
Yagize ati, mu bimwe byatangajwe na CNN mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare, " uretse icyorezo cya grippe, nta wundi virusi yo mu muvuduko w'umwuka yakurikiranwe kuva yatangira kugeza igihe ikomeje gukwirakwira ku isi hose".
Gabrels yavuze ko hari abantu benshi bafite uburwayi bw'icyorezo cya Coronavirus, ariko ko nta muntu n'umwe ufite uburwayi bw'icyorezo.
Yakomeje agira ati "Nta kindi gihe twigeze tubona icyorezo gishobora gukomerezwa icyarimwe".
Icyorezo gishya cy'icyorezo kiza nyuma y'icyemezo cya OMS cyo gutangaza ko hari icyihutirwa mu buzima rusange gifite impungenge mpuzamahanga mu kwezi kwa mbere.
Umuyobozi w'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe indwara z'ubumara n'icyorezo, Dr. Anthony Fauci, yavuze ko iki cyorezo "mu magambo make, kigenda kirushaho kuzamba".
Kugeza kuwa gatanu, Associated Press yatangaje ko ku isi hose hari nibura abantu 126,000 banduye COVID-19, bituma hapfa abantu barenga 4600.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019-20 ni icyorezo cy'indwara ya Coronavirus (COVID-19) cyatewe n'indwara ikomeye y'umugera wa Coronavirus yo mu mpumuro (SARS-CoV-2).
Iki cyorezo cyamenyekanye mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu Bushinwa mu kwezi kwa cumi na kabiri mu mwaka wa 2019, cyatangajwe ku wa 30 Mutarama 2020 nk'ihungabana rikomeye ry'ubuzima rusange rifite impungenge mpuzamahanga, ndetse cyatangajwe nk'icyorezo ku wa 11 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 1.61 banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 210 n'uturere, bituma abantu bagera ku 97,000 bapfa.
Abantu bagera ku 364,000 barakize.
Umubare w'abapfa ufatwa n'abantu benshi mu Bushinwa ni 4%, mu gihe ku isi hose utangira ku 13.04% muri Algeria ugera ku 0.08% muri Nouvelle-Zélande.
Ibimenyetso bisanzwe birimo gusinzira, guhumeka nabi no guhumeka nabi.
Ingorane z'ikibazo zishobora kuba zirimo uburwayi bw'ibihaha n'ibimenyetso by'ububabare bw'ubuhumekero.
Igihe cyo kugaragaza ibimenyetso ni iminsi itanu, ariko gishobora kuba hagati y'iminsi ibiri na 14.
Nta rukingo cyangwa umuti wa virusi bizwi.
Uburyo bw'ibanze bwo kuvura ibimenyetso n'ubuvuzi ni ubufasha. Uburyo bw'ibanze bw'umuganga buvuga ko umuntu agomba kwirinda gukaraba intoki, guhisha akanwa mu gihe arimo kunywa, kwirinda abandi, no kwita ku bantu bakekwaho kuba banduye no kwivuza.
Ku isi hose, abategetsi bagiye bagaragaza ko bahagarariye binyuze mu gushyiraho amategeko agenga ingendo, gushyira mu kato, kubuza ingendo, kugenzura ibyago by'abakurikirana, no gufunga ibigo.
Icyorezo cyatumye isi yose ihungabana mu by'imibereho n'imibereho, igatinda cyangwa ikanga ibikorwa by'imikino, amadini, politiki n'umuco, kandi bigatuma abantu benshi batakaza ibikoresho byabo bitewe n'uko bagura.
Amashuri na kaminuza, yaba ku rwego rw'igihugu cyangwa rwo mu gihugu, yafunzwe mu bihugu 193, bigira ingaruka ku kigero cy'abanyeshuri bagera kuri 99.4% ku isi.
Amakuru atari yo kuri iyi virusi yagiye akwirakwira kuri internet, kandi hari n'ubwoba ku banyamahanga no kurenganywa ku baturage b'u Bushinwa, abandi bantu b'amoko n'imiterere y'iburasirazuba n'uburasirazuba bw'u Bushinwa, abandi bantu bo mu turere turimo ubwandu bw'iyi virusi.
Kubera ingendo zigabanutse n'ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi bikomeye bifunze, umwuka wahumanyijwe n'umwuka wa CO2 wagabanutse.
Abategetsi b'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu Bushinwa (umurwa mukuru w'akarere ka Hubei) batangaje ko ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, hari abantu benshi banduye ibicurane by'ibihaha, batangira gukora iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama 2020.
Ibibazo byinshi byagiye bibaho byari bifitanye isano n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu mazi by'i Hawa, bityo hari icyizere ko virusi ishobora kuba ari iy'inyamaswa.
Virusi yatumye iki cyorezo cyakwirakwira mu buryo bw'ubudahangarwa yitwa SARS-CoV-2, virusi nshya ivumbuwe ifitanye isano na coronavirus ya coronavirus ya nyamugigima, coronavirus ya pangolin, SARS-CoV. Umuntu wamenyekanye cyane ko yari afite ibimenyetso hanyuma akaza kurwara ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019, uwo muntu nta sano n'ubucuruzi bw'inyama nshya.
Mu bantu ba mbere bavuzwe mu kwezi kwa cumi na kumwe mu 2019, bibiri bya gatatu by'ababa bari mu isoko ry'inyama zitanduye.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe 2020, raporo itari yemewe yo mu kinyamakuru cya South China Monring Post yagaragaje ko hari umuntu umwe w'imyaka 55 wo mu karere ka Hubei wanduye iki cyorezo ku itariki ya 17 Ugushyingo 2019, bikaba bishoboka ko ari we wa mbere. Ku itariki ya 26 Gashyantare 2020, OMS yavuze ko, uko umubare w'abanduye mu Bushinwa wagendaga ugabanuka, ariko mu Butaliyani, Iran na Koreya y'Epfo ukazamuka mu buryo butunguranye, umubare w'abanduye hanze y'u Bushinwa warenze umubare w'abanduye mu Bushinwa ku ncuro ya mbere.
Hari igihe abantu benshi batavugwaho, cyane cyane mu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje.
Kugeza ku wa 26 Gashyantare, umubare muto w'abanduye wabonetse mu rubyiruko, abari munsi y'imyaka 19 ku isi yose wari 2.4% by'abanduye. Umujyanama mu by'ubumenyi w'u Bwongereza, Patrick Valance, yahanuye ko 60% by'abatuye u Bwongereza bagomba kwandura mbere y'uko uburwayi bw'ubwandu bw'abantu bubaho.
Abanduye bagaragaza umubare w'abantu bagizwe abanduye kuri COVID-19, kandi bagaragazwa ko bageze kuri COVID-19 bakurikije gahunda z'ubugenzuzi.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyaragennye abantu barenga 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi ibihugu byinshi byari bifite politiki yemewe yo kwirinda abantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje gusa, urugero nk'u Butaliyani, U Buholandi, Esipanye na Suisse.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku wa 16 Werurwe bwagaragaje ko mu Bushinwa, kugeza ku wa 23 Mutarama, nta kigero cy'ibyago bya COVID-19 cyabonetse kigera kuri 86%, kandi ko ibyo bitanduye bitigeze byandikwa ari byo byateje 79% by'ibyago byakozwe.
Iperereza ry'ibarura ryasohowe ku wa 30 Werurwe ryavuze ko umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani warenze cyane umubare w'abamaze kumenyekana.
Igitekerezo cya mbere cy'umubare w'abanduye (R0) kuri COVID-19 cyari hagati ya 1.4 na 2.4.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara muri Amerika, bwagaragaje ko ari 5.7.
Abenshi mu bafite COVID-19 barakira.
Mu bantu bataza gukira, kuva igihe ibimenyetso byigaragarijemo kugeza igihe bapfiriye, byibura hagati y'iminsi 6 na 41, ubusanzwe bikaba ari iminsi 14.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, COVID-19 imaze guhitana abantu bagera ku 97.000.
Mu Bushinwa, kugeza ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, 80% by'abapfuye bari hejuru y'imyaka 60, naho 75% bari bafite izindi ndwara z'ubuzima nk'indwara z'umutima na diyabete. Umubare w'abapfuye ku bushake bahitanywe na COVID-19 ubusanzwe ugaragaza abapfuye bageragejwe ko banduye COVID-19 nk'uko byemezwa n'amategeko.
Umubare w'abapfa mu by'ukuri bahitanwe na COVID-19 ushobora kuba ari munini cyane, kuko ushobora kuba ugizwe n'abantu bapfuye bageragezwa - urugero, mu ngo z'abageze mu za bukuru, n'ibindi.
Amakuru yatanzwe mu Butaliyani avuga ko umubare w'abapfuye mu gihe cy'icyorezo wikubye inshuro 4-5 umubare w'abapfa ba COVID.
Umuvugizi wa US Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) yavuze ko " tuzi ko [umubare w'abapfuye watangajwe] ari ibintu bitagaragara, " itangazo riherekejwe n'inkuru z'ibitarimo kugenzura muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika. Akenshi ibyo bitigiri bitagaragara mu gihe cy'ibiza, nk'icyorezo cya influenza ya N1H1 yo mu 2009.
Icyorezo cya mbere cy'ubwandu hanze y'u Bushinwa cyabaye ku itariki ya 1 Gashyantare muri Philippines, n'icyambere cy'ubwandu hanze ya Aziya cyabaye ku itariki ya 14 Gashyantare mu Bufaransa.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, hanze y'u Bushinwa, hapfuye abantu barenga 12 buri umwe muri bo muri Irani, Koreya y'Epfo n'u Butaliyani.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, ibihugu n'uturere birenga 40 byatangaje ko habayeho ubwandu, ku mugabane wose uretse Antarctica. Hari ingamba nyinshi z'ingenzi zigamije kugabanya ubwandu.
Ibipimo bihinduka bitewe n'ahantu n'igihe, kandi bigira ingaruka ku kigero cy'imibonano, ubwiza bw'uburyo bwo kwita ku buzima, uburyo bwo kuvurwa, igihe kuva indwara itangirira kubaho, n'ibimenyetso by'abaturage nk'imyaka, igitsina n'ubuzima rusange. Imibare y'abapfuye igaragaza umubare w'abapfuye bagabanutse ku mubare w'abarwayi mu gihe runaka.
Ishingiye ku mibare ya Johns Hopkins University, umubare w'abapfuye ku isi ni 6.0% (97,039/1,617,204) kugeza ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020.
Umubare uhinduka bitewe n'akarere.
Mu Bushinwa, igipimo cy'ubwandu bw'abantu bapfa cyagabanutse kiva kuri 17.3 (ku bafite intangiriro y'ibimenyetso kuva ku itariki ya 1-10 Mutarama 2020*) kigera kuri 0.7% (ku bafite intangiriro y'ibimenyetso nyuma y'itariki ya 1 Gashyantare 2020). Ibindi bipimo birimo igipimo cy'ubwandu bw'abantu bapfa (CFR), kigaragaza igipimo cy'abantu bapfuye bazize iyo ndwara, n'igitigiri cy'abapfa bazize iyo ndwara (IFR), kigaragaza igipimo cy'abantu bapfa bazize iyo ndwara (bamaze gusuzumwa cyangwa batazizwe).
Ibipimo ntabwo ari iby'igihe kandi bigenzura abaturage bwite banduye mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi.
Hari abanyeshuri bagerageje kubara imibare y'abaturage.
Ikigo cya kaminuza ya Oxford gishinzwe ubuvuzi gishingiye ku bimenyetso giteganya ko umubare w'abapfa bahitanwa n'icyorezo muri rusange uzaba uri hagati ya 0.1% na 0.39%.
Ibipimo by'abagereranywa hejuru byemejwe mu buryo buhuje n'ibyavuye mu igenzura rya mbere riherutse gukorwa ku buryo bufatiweho rya COVID-19 mu Budage, ndetse n'ubushakashatsi bw'ibarurishamibare bugaragaza ingaruka z'iryo genzura ku byerekanwa na CFR.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryemeza ko icyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa.
Igihe cyo gutangira no kurangiza icyorezo ntabwo biramenyekana kandi bishobora guhinduka bitewe n'aho biri.
Massey Bunny wo muri Penn State University yagize ati "Utabimenye, ubwandu bushobora kuba bwinshi, hanyuma bukagenda bugabanuka iyo indwara itakiriho.
Ariko ntushobora guhita ubimenya neza".
Umujyanama mukuru mu by'ubuvuzi wa leta y'u Bushinwa, Zhong Nchan, yavuze ko "bishobora kurangira mu kwezi kwa gatandatu" niba ibihugu byose bishobora kwitegura gukurikiza inama z'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima ku bijyanye n'ingamba zo guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'iyi virus.
Ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, Adam Kucharsky wo muri Kaminuza y'u Bwongereza y'Ubuvuzi bw'Imyuka n'Ibirere yavuze ko SARS-CoV-2 "izamara umwaka umwe cyangwa ibiri".
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Neil Ferguson muri Imperial College of Leadership, kwirinda abantu no kwirinda abandi bizakenerwa "kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rubonetse (bishoboka ko ruzaba rumaze amezi 18 cyangwa arenga)".
William Shaffner wo muri Vanderbilt University yagize ati "Ntekereza ko bishoboka ko iyi virusi ya Corona - kubera ko ari icyorezo cy'indwara nyinshi - izaba ari indwara itandura rwose" kandi "ishobora kuba indwara y'ikirere, igaruka buri mwaka".
