Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bidakorwa ku buryo bufatiweho, kandi abantu banduye bashobora kuba badafite ibimenyetso.
Ibimenyetso bibiri bikunze kugaragara ni up (88%) na coke yumye (68%).
Ibindi bimenyetso bidasanzwe birimo kurwara indwara y'ihindagurika, guhumeka nabi, gutakaza ibyiyumvo by'incuro nyinshi, guhumeka nabi, kurwara mu ngingo no mu ngingo, kurwara, kurwara, kurira, guhindagurika, amaraso y'uruhu, gusama, cyangwa ubura bw'uruhu. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) rivuga ko kimwe cya gatandatu cy'abantu bose baba barwaye indwara ikomeye kandi ko bafite ibibazo byo guhumeka.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyemeza ibimenyetso by'impanuka nk'ubuhumekero, ububabare cyangwa umuvuduko w'ubuhumekero, guhungabana mu buryo butunguranye, ibibazo byo kugenda, no guhanagura mu maso cyangwa mu kanwa; kwitabwaho kwa muganga byihutirwa nihaba hari ibyo bimenyetso. Kubura uburwayi bishobora gutera indwara y'ubuhumekero bw'ibihaha, guhangana n'ihungabana ry'ubuhumekero, uburozi bw'amaraso n'urupfu.
Bamwe mu barwaye bashobora kuba badafite ibimenyetso, nta bimenyetso bya kliniki bihari ariko bagakorwaho ubushakashatsi kugira ngo bagaragaze ko bafite ibimenyetso by'ubwandu, bityo abashakashatsi bagatanga inama ko abantu bagiranye isano rya bugufi n'abantu bafite ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bagomba gukurikiranwa cyane no gukorerwa ubwirinzi kugira ngo bakwirinde indwara.
Ubushinwa buvuga ko igipimo cy'uburwayi bw'ibimenyetso kizaba kiri hagati ya 44% na 44%.
