Ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe, hari abantu 32,308 banduye muri New York City, n'abantu 672 bahitanwe na virusi. Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zifite umubare munini w'abantu banduye virusi ya Coronavirusi kurusha ikindi gihugu cyose ku isi, harimo Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Ku itariki ya 8 Mata, hari abantu 400,335 banduye muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, n'abantu 12,841 bapfuye.
Nkuko byatangajwe n'ibitangazamakuru ku wa 30 Werurwe, Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika Trump yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwirinda imyidagaduro kugeza ku wa 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, UNSS Comfort, yafashe ubwato bw'ibitaro bwari bufite ibitanda bigera ku 1000 i New York.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zabonye abantu 884 bapfuye bazize Coronavirus mu masaha 24.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata muri Leta ya New York, abantu barenga 100,000 barwaye. Ibiro by'ibanze by'abapolisi by'Amerika byashidikanyijweho kubera ko nta cyo byagezeho mu guhangana n'icyo cyorezo no kugenzura amakuru binyuze mu guhamagarira abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga gufatanya mu gusobanura no gusohora amakuru y'ibanze ku byerekeye iyi virusi hamwe n'ibiro by'icegera cya Perezida Mike Pence.
Muri rusange, kwakira ubuyobozi bwa Trump kuri iki kibazo byatandukanye mu mashyaka y'amashyaka.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika n'abandi bantu bashishikajwe n'ibyo, banenze ko Amerika ari yo ikoresha mu kwinjiza ibintu by'ingenzi, urugero nk'ibikoresho by'ibanze by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa.
Isesengura ry'uburyo bwo gutwara umwuka ryakoreshejwe mu kumenya no guhanura uburyo bwo gukwirakwira, ryasohowe mu kinyamakuru cya TravelMedicine mu kwezi kwa Mutarama 2020.
Ukurikije amakuru yo mu 2018 yavuye muri International Air Transport Board, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo, na Taipei byagize umubare munini w'abagenzi bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byasizweho kuba ahantu hazwi cyane ho gutembera mu gihugu cya Wuhan.
Bali yatangaje ko ari yo ifite ubushobozi buke cyane mu mijyi 20 ikunze kugaragara cyane mu bijyanye no kwitegura, mu gihe mijyi yo muri Australia yagaragaye ko ifite ubushobozi buke cyane. Australia yatangaje gahunda yo guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) ku wa 7 Gashyantare.
Ibi byatangaje ko hari byinshi byasobanutse kuri COVID-19, kandi ko Australia igamije kugenzura imipaka no gushyikirana mu gusubiza iki cyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, hatangajwe ko hari ikibazo cy'umutekano muke mu bantu muri Ositaraliya.
Kubera ko hari ingendo z'indege z'abaturage z'i Wuhan n'i Hobi zagiye zihagarikwa, ibihugu byinshi byateganyaga gusubiza abaturage n'abakozi ba diplomasi zabo muri ako karere, cyane cyane mu ndege z'igihugu, ndetse no gusobanura ibyo byavuzwe n'abayobozi b'u Bushinwa.
Canada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Australia, Ufaransa, Argentine, Ubudage, na Thailand ni bimwe mu bihugu bya mbere byateganyije gusubiza abaturage babo mu byabo.
Pakistan yavuze ko itazagarura abaturage bayo mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 7 Gashyantare, Brazil yashubijeho 34 mu Banyaburezili cyangwa abagize umuryango wabo, harimo bane b'Abanyapolonye, umwe w'Umushinwa, n'undi w'Umuhindi.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, Ubushinwa n'u Buhinde bahagaze muri Polonye, mu gihe indege y'igihugu cya Brazil yahagaritse mbere yo gukomeza urugendo rwe yerekeza muri Brazil.
Abaturage ba Brazil bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brazil.
Kuri uwo munsi, Abakanada 215 (176 ku ndege ya mbere, 39 ku ndege ya kabiri yemewe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika) basubijwe i Wuhan muri Trenton CFB kugira ngo bashyire mu kato icyumweru kimwe.
Ku itariki ya 11/2, indi ndege yo mu bwoko bwa 185 ya Canada yahanuye i Wan ku kigo cya gisirikare cya Canada i Trenton.
Guverinoma ya Australia yashyize abaturage 277 mu kigo cy'ubutabazi cya Christmas Island, cyari cyatanzwe nk'ahantu ho gushyirwamo abantu mu kato, aho bari kumara iminsi 14.
Ikigo cy'indege cya New Zealand Air Transport Force cyageze i Auckland ku itariki ya 5/2; abagenzi (bamwe muri bo bari muri Australia no mu nyanja ya Pasifika) bari mu kato ku kigo cya Hongpao, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
