Ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa Coronavirus byafatiwe ku barwayi bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo, bagaragazwa n'ubushyuhe, bashyikirizwa ubugenzuzi bukomeye kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Gusa abaturage bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaye ko badafite ubwandu mu bipimo byabo, ni bo bonyine basubijwe mu gihugu cyabo.
Ibizamini byemezaga ko abaturage bose ba Afurika y'Epfo, harimo abasirikare, abagenzi, abakozi bo mu mahoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare, bari bafite inshingano zo kurinda abantu mu gisirikare.
