Iyo hari ubwirinzi bukomeye mu baturage, nubwo hari uburyo bwo kwirinda imibonano mpuzabitsina, ikiruhuko cyo kwagura ikiruhuko cy'ishuri gishobora kubonwa. Ku bw'amategeko agenga ubuyobozi bw'igihugu ashyigikira ibikorwa by'umunsi w'akazi, ibyago by'ubuzima by'ibanze bifatwaho nabi cyane na CDC.
