Ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin 2 (ACE2) ni ingirabuzima fatizo igaragara ku gice cyo hanze cy'ingirabuzima fatizo z'ingirabuzima fatizo ziri mu maraso, mu maraso, mu mutima, mu bwonko no mu mara.
ACE2 ikumira ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin-indemita (ACE) ikorana na yo igabanya ingirabuzima fatizo y'ibanze (Angon-1-7) ikongeraho ingirabuzima fatizo (Angon-1-7) ikaba ari umuti utera icyizere mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 kandi ikora nk'inzira yo kwinjira mu bice by'ingirabuzima fatizo bya virusi zimwe na zimwe za coronavirusi.
Guhindura umuntu kuri iyo enzyme akenshi bisobanurwa nk' hACE2.
Igitoki cy'umura wa zinc cyitwa angiotensin cy'ibanze kirimo umura wa zinc w'icyuma kigaragara ku gice cy'imbere cy'umura wa zinc n'ibindi bice by'ingirabuzimafatizo.
Poroteyine ACE2 igizwe n'umushyikirizi N w'urubuga rw'umushyikirizi wa poroteyine ya peptide M2 n'umushyikirizi C wifatanyije na acide aminike y'umushyikirizi ukomeye.
ACE ni ubwoko bwonyine bwa I bw'imiterere ya poroteyine, ifite ingirabuzimafatizo ikora ku ngirabuzimafatizo ku gice cy'ingirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso ndetse no ku bindi bice by'umubiri.
Icyuma cy'ingenzi cy'umurambo cya ACE2 cyatandukanyijwe n'umubiri w'ingenzi, cyitwa shedesis, gihinduka umubiri w'ingenzi mu maraso, ugasohoka ukajya mu maraso.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifite uruhu rw'ibinyabuzima cyane cyane mu bice by'umubiri by'ubwoko bwa cyclocyte, mu nda, mu maraso no mu maraso, ndetse no mu bice byinshi by'umubiri harimo ingirabuzima fatizo y'amaraso.
Nanone, ACE2 yitwa mRNA iboneka mu bwonko, mu bwonko bwo hagati, mu bwonko bwo hasi no mu bwonko bwo hasi.
Umurimo wa mbere wa ACE2 ni ugushyira hamwe kw'ibanze kwa ACE.
ACE ikora kimwe mu byatuma umuntu ahindura ingofero ebyiri z'ingofero mu maraso.
ACE2 ikoresha imyuka ya carboxyl-thermial amino acid phenylalanine ikoreshwa mu kuvura imyuka ya anigotensin II (Asp-Arg-Bal-Tyr-IIe-His-Pro-Phe) na hydrolyses (vasodilator angiotensin (1 - 7, H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Lle-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora no guhagarika ingufu z'izindi peptide nyinshi nk'izitwa -[des-Arg9] bradykinin, apelin neurotensin, dynorp hin A, ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi ikora cyane mu guhindura amini acidi SLC6A19 kandi yabonetse mu ndwara ya Hartnap.
Nk'imiterere y'imiterere y'imiterere y'umubiri, ACE2 ikora nk'ikirindiro cy'ingenzi cyo kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za virusi zimwe na zimwe za coronavirusi, urugero nka HcoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (iyi virusi iteza SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (iyi virusi iteza COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, guhuza S1 binding ya SARS-CoV-2 na SARS-CoV-2 ku cyuma cyitwa ACE2 ku gice cy'ingirabuzimafatizo, bigatuma ikinyabuzima kinini cy'umunyururu n'umunyururu bihindura virusi na enzyme muri endosome iri mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Hari igitekerezo cy'uko kugabanya ACE2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo bishobora gufasha kurwanya iyi ndwara.
Icyakora, hari amatorero y'abahanga mu by'imikorere y'umubiri n'abakora imyitozo ngororamubiri, bagaragaza ko buri gihe hari ibipimo by'ubuvuzi bw'indwara ya ACE n'ubuvuzi bwa ARB.
Ibirimo gukorwa n'ubushakashatsi n'ibyagezweho byasohotse ku itariki ya 11, 2020 mu itangazo ry'ibanze, byagaragaje ko "kwifashishwa kwa ACE y'ubushakashatsi byateye imbere cyane ku buryo byatumye habaho kugabanuka k'ibipimo by'ubwandu ku kigero cya 34% mu gihe byakorwaga".
Byongeye kandi, "ibyago byo kurwara indwara zikomeye z'ibihaha byagabanutse cyane ku barwayi bavurwa na ACE inhibitors, cyane cyane abafite indwara z'ibihaha, cyane cyane abafite uburwayi bw'umutima utagira ubwonko.
Gukoresha ACE inhibitors byafashije mu guhangana n'indwara y'ibihaha ya pneumonia ifitanye isano n'iki cyorezo, nubwo ibisubizo byari bifite ubuzima buke kurusha ibyago rusange byo kurwara ibihaha bya pneumonia.
